    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>American 19th-century clocks generally resembling an acorn in outline and available in shelf, wall, and mantel styles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
